'''Land crawlers''' were vehicles well-equipped to handle the harsh terrain of [[Ambria/Legends|Ambria]]. They had two front wheels and four rear wheels, the latter forming two caterpillar tracks. They had large cargo holds, often used by [[Scavenger/Legends|salvagers]] to carry discovered "treasures." The [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lord]] [[Darth Bane/Legends|Darth Bane]] drove one such vehicle when he found [[Mikki]]'s family, who were using a land crawler too, for salvaging. Bane murdered the family before driving his crawler to the [[Caleb's hut|home]] of the healer [[Caleb]].

